Sentencas: Anode-supported planar solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with an active area of 81 cm(2) (9 cm x 9 cm) and nano-structured La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta+Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 (LSCF + YSZ) composite cathodes are successfully fabricated by tape casting, screen printing, co-firing and solution impregnation, and tested using H-2 fuel and air oxidant at various flow rates.
Titulo: Performance of large-scale anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with impregnated La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ+Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes

Sentencas: Maximum power densities of 437 and 473 mW cm(-2) are achieved at 750 degrees C by loading 0.6 and 1.3 mg cm(-2) of LSCF in the composite cathodes, respectively.
Titulo: Performance of large-scale anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with impregnated La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ+Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes

Sentencas: The gas flow rates, particularly the air, have a significant effect on the cell performance.
Titulo: Performance of large-scale anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with impregnated La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ+Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes

Sentencas: Cell performance degradation with time is also observed, which is considered to be associated with the growth and coalescence of the nanosized LSCF particles in the composite cathode.
Titulo: Performance of large-scale anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with impregnated La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ+Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes

Sentencas: The use of the LSCF cathode in combination with YSZ electrolyte without a Gd-doped CeO2 (GDC) buffer layer is proved to be applicable in large cells, even though the thermal stability of the nanosized LSCF needs to be further improved.
Titulo: Performance of large-scale anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with impregnated La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-δ+Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 composite cathodes
